Conceal a 5-foot entangling or
impaling trap.
Entangling Trap: Test Survival
vs. Cognitive, roll 2d4 impact
damage. Target is Immobilized
and the area becomes difficult
terrain.
Impaling Trap: Test Survival
vs. Physical, roll 2d4 keen
damage. Target is Afflicted
[vital damage equal to 3 +
your ranks in Survival].